---
title: Apricot Ginger Chicken Lightning Prep
description: This chicken is our jam! No, seriously. Pan-seared chicken in a fresh ginger and apricot jam sauce is here to cure all your weeknight dinner woes. It’s sweet, savory, aromatic, and all-around delicious. Plus, the excitement only continues with the sides. Chicken pairs perfectly with crisp roasted green beans and fluffy, buttery rice. Jam out.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/apricot-ginger-chicken-457dd97d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/apricot-ginger-chicken-5dfd029c7107e12c983f624a-4e1fb341.pdf
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/apricot-ginger-chicken-5dfd029c7107e12c983f624a
cuisine: North America
time required: 25 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 570 kcal
  fat: 21 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
